name: Top Scary Pranks Challenge
summary:
Top Scary Pranks: The Ultimate VR Jumpscare Tool!

Top Scary Pranks is not your typical game—it’s the ultimate way to prank and scare your friends and family in VR. With immersive puzzles and perfectly timed jumpscares, this experience guarantees screams and laughs in equal measure.

The adventure begins as a casual puzzle game set in a peculiar environment. Players choose a difficulty level and face a series of brain-teasing challenges using touch controls or hand tracking. But beware—on the third...
